PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food of ROBERT M. COLPITTS, of Fredericton, New Brunswick, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Farm Credit Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years, in the place of Edward William Clark, whose term has expired.
